   "source": [
    "## 7 · Where does it (mis)route?\n",
    "\n",
    "A confusion matrix over 8 queues is readable. We look at the fine-tuned model and\n",
    "then extract the **most common misrouting pairs** — the operational failure mode\n",
    "(a ticket bounced to the wrong team)."
   ]
  },
